data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT!  Great tax rate and price! NO SURVEY available.  Welcome to this stunning home nestled in the highly sought-after Summerlyn community of Leander, Texas. This property offers an exceptional living experience with its prime location!  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the pristine condition of this home!  Many recent updates to the home include carpet in the two secondary bedrooms-8/23, vinyl plank flooring-8/23 and new disposal and microwave in 8/23.  Other updates include full interior wall paint 8/23 (excluding closets and baseboards) and a roof and fence installed in 2021.  The kitchen boasts generous counter space making meal preparation a breeze, and a pantry area to keep your culinary essentials organized.  Additionally, a dedicated dining area is conveniently located in the kitchen, providing a comfortable space for family meals and gatherings. Outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the nice sized backyard, perfect for hosting outdoor activities, barbecues, or simply enjoying a peaceful retreat. The covered patios in front and back offer a shady spot to relax on sunny days or unwind in the evenings. The community amenities, such as a pool, basketball courts, playscape, and green space, add to the appeal of this fantastic location. Conveniently situated near major roads-183 and Hwy. 29, schools, shopping, and entertainment. Highly acclaimed and highly rated Leander ISD!! Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a home in a great community, with fantastic amenities, in a fast-growing area. Schedule a showing today and make this house your new home!
